# Phase 5 acceptance criteria

Do not move to Phase 6 unless all of these are true:

* People panel is populated, even if counts are zero
* `Review Possible Merges` opens the merge review path
* `Show Unnamed Clusters` opens the unnamed-cluster review path
* `Show All People` expands or opens the legacy People manager
* `People Tools` delegates to legacy People tools
* `History`, `Undo`, `Redo`, `Expand` delegate to legacy handlers
* legacy People section remains underneath as fallback
* no regressions in merge/undo/review workflows
* `google_legacy` remains untouched

